::container
### Variants
The primary `Button` contains an animation effect.

~~~html
<backify-button>Primary</backify-button>
<backify-button type="solid">Solid</backify-button>
<backify-button type="outline">Outline</backify-button>
~~~
:::
:::container
### Icons
Add icon to `Button`.

~~~html
<backify-button type="solid" icon="heart">Heart Icon</backify-button>
<backify-button type="icon" icon="heart" tt-pos="top">Top Tooltip</backify-button>
~~~
:::
